### Variables Globales
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 1. Probar Salud del Sistema
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

---

### 2. Login de Usuario (Obtener Token)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@odontoshop.com",
    "password": "admin123"
}

---

### 3. Probar Dashboard Protegido (Requiere Login previo)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..2dYFHyMy_73I_BKg__tLN3CWcw7G-v2QyHWY8gps9B8
---

### 4. Crear un Producto de Odontología
# Nota: Si aún no creas el módulo de productos, esto dará 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "name": "Turbina Dental Pro",
    "description": "Alta velocidad con luz LED",
    "price": 250.00,
    "stock": 15
}

---

### 5. Ver Perfil de Usuario (Me)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..2dYFHyMy_73I_BKg__tLN3CWcw7G-v2QyHWY8gps9B8